- `test:traffic-notification-claim-guards`
- `test:agent-report-state-guards`
- D017 锁、推进顺序与复用机制静态检查
- `git diff --check`

因“两文件限定”，未修改现有守卫源文件；未碰 schema/package、并行文件，未 commit/push/发版。
